    <description>Entity Framework Core extensions for SecureORM. Transparent order-preserving encoding via attributes and value converters. Query encrypted data with ORDER BY, exact match, prefix search, and range queries — without decryption.</description>
    <tags>efcore entity-framework encryption encoding ope order-preserving security database query orm</tags>
